column1: Claimant data by constituency: JSA claimants and Universal Credit claimants required to seek work, December 2016

Notes: Figures include JSA claimants and people claiming Universal Credit (UC) who are required to seek work. UC figures are provisional. All data are rounded to the nearest five, except for data on claims by type (JSA claimants only; UC claimants only). The number of JSA claimants and the number of UC claimants may not sum to the total claimant count as data are taken from different sources and are independently rounded.
Claimant rate is the proportion of the economically active population aged 16-64 (as estimated by the Library) who are claiming JSA or claiming UC and required to seek work.
